'''Makomo eMvurwi''' (Mvurwi Ranges) anotambanuka kwenhambwe inokwana 160km kubva pana [[Rwizi Manyame]]. Anokwira kusvika pa[[hukwidza]] hunoita 1,752m. Makomo aya ndiyo anowumba chikamu chiri ku[[Maodzanyemba]] chenzvimbo inocherwa mugodhi unowanikwa [[chrome]]. Maguta ari pedyo neMakomo eMvurwi ndiwo anonzi: [[Darwendale]]; [[Maryland junction]] ne[[Kildonan]].
